(195, 38, '0', '商家远程防骗，请用招商兴业', '+', 0, 0, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '', NULL, '<p>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:18px;"><span style="font-size:16px;"><span style="font-size:12px;"><span style="font-size:10px;"></span></span></span></span><span style="line-height:1.5;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="line-height:1.5;">因为招商、兴业付款页面中有一个二级商户名字，就是你本人的实名认证的淘宝支付宝号，一般是你的姓名或者店铺名，在支付宝没有实名无法完成收款。所以只要认准了你的名字与店铺名字，就没有问题。其它银行只有一级名字，就是支付宝，看不到二级名字。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="line-height:1.5;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="line-height:1.5;">商家远程付款防骗步骤，</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<span>（1）先让刷手在电脑上打开我的淘宝，并登陆。</span><br />\r\n<span>（2）QQ远程后你自己在购物车里面或者在已买宝贝里面提交付款，不要让刷手找出付款页面来，你直接付款，以防他修改了付款页面。</span><br />\r\n<span>（3）在这个过程中仔细看好订单信息，并且看好电脑的屏幕，和你正常淘宝购物时，显示的内容是否一样。</span><br />\r\n<span>（4）扫码成功后首先核对金额是否一致，然后核对自己的手机银行，详情或者二级商户那里是不是自己的支付宝实名认证的姓名或公司名称。</span><br />\r\n<p>\r\n	（5）在QQ远程以前，最好你先登陆你的手机银行，并且尽量不要让手机银行进入屏保，20秒左右点一次手机屏幕就可以。开始操作后，你再找到手机银行再进入，容易分散精力。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	如果骗子售中退款，商家同意退款即可，资金是原路返回到商家的招商、兴业银行。如果骗子申请售后退款，就是确认收货后退款，请不要同意退款，证明自己是刷单即可，切勿同意退款，否则资金会退到骗子支付宝。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src="/attached/image/20170406/20170406223546_93150.jpg" width="700" height="346" alt="" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src="/attached/image/20170406/20170406223723_22311.jpg" width="700" height="366" alt="" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src="/attached/image/20170406/20170406223840_54597.jpg" width="700" height="400" alt="" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src="/attached/image/20170406/20170406223920_86637.jpg" width="700" height="400" alt="" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<img src="/attached/image/20170406/20170406223955_46321.jpg" width="700" height="392" alt="" /><img src="/attached/image/20170406/20170406224043_37566.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/attached/image/20170406/20170406224053_45746.jpg" alt="" /> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-size:32px;line-height:48px;">以下内容是关于兴业银行的</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:32px;line-height:48px;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:32px;line-height:48px;"><img src="/attached/image/20170406/20170406224302_95664.jpg" width="678" height="426" alt="" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:32px;line-height:48px;"><img src="/attached/image/20170406/20170406224421_65740.jpg" alt="" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:32px;line-height:48px;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:32px;line-height:48px;"> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	第（3）步，先不要输入支付密码和动态口令，直接点击下一步，IOS系统的可以直接下一步，因为直接点下一步等于没输入卡号，可以看到【二级商户】\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	第（4）步，你可以看到你的订单详细信息，二级商户就是你的卖家支付宝的名字，或者企业名称。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n	<br />\r\n</div>\r\n<span>安卓系统的如果不能直接点下一步的，那就故意输错一次验证码，当你故意输错一次二维码的时候。你的订单详情信息就出现了↓</span><br />\r\n<p>\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:32px;line-height:48px;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:32px;line-height:48px;"><img src="/attached/image/20170406/20170406224446_66004.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/attached/image/20170406/20170406224508_75631.jpg" alt="" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="line-height:48px;"><span>第（5）步，最后当我们检查完订单详情，确定信息无误的时候，直接返回，重新输入动态码，支付码付款。要看清楚二级商户。</span><br />\r\n<span>不要再去重新扫描二维码付款了，避免二次扫描的二维码是被切换过的页面的二维码。直接点击返回之前的界面输入支付密码和动态吗进行付款就可以了。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:32px;line-height:48px;"><img src="/attached/image/20170406/20170406224721_72881.jpg" alt="" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:32px;line-height:48px;"><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:32px;line-height:48px;"><span style="font-size:32px;line-height:48px;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;以下内容是骗子的实例</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:32px;line-height:48px;"><span style="font-size:32px;line-height:48px;"><br />\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:32px;line-height:48px;"><img src="/attached/image/20170406/20170406224824_60161.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/attached/image/20170406/20170406224838_75631.jpg" alt="" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="font-size:32px;line-height:48px;"><img src="/attached/image/20170406/20170406224857_66744.jpg" alt="" /><img src="/attached/image/20170406/20170406224905_94491.jpg" alt="" /><br />\r\n</span> \r\n</p>', '', '', NULL, 1, NULL, 1, 1, 0, 1491447086, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 0),
