(184, 38, '0', '关于收货时间到后物流未签收的新规', '+', 0, 0, NULL, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 1, '', NULL, '<h3 style="font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:1.17em;font-family:微软雅黑;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#444444;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-size:18.72px;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#FF0000;"><strong><strong>平台禁止接手方物流未到在淘宝确认收货，但商家在选择时间上亦有责任，选择的太短，会给双方都造成困扰。</strong></strong></span> \r\n</h3>\r\n<h3 style="font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:1.17em;font-family:微软雅黑;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#444444;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-size:18.72px;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#FF0000;"><strong><strong>所以</strong>新规的出台是为了规范双方的行为，减少此类投诉！</strong></span> \r\n</h3>\r\n<p style="font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#444444;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#444444;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#FF0000;"><strong>处理范围：</strong></span>针对任务<span style="font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#FF0000;"><strong>收货时间到了</strong></span><strong>但是淘宝<span style="font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#FF0000;">物流信息还未被签收</span></strong>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#444444;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#444444;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<strong><span style="font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#FF0000;">处理方案</span></strong>：\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#444444;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<strong><span style="font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#FF0000;">1、官方补偿方案</span></strong>：根据<strong>超时<span style="font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#FF0000;">天数</span>补偿</strong>，<strong>超时<span style="font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#FF0000;">24小时后</span>开始计算</strong>，如若<strong>24小时内物流到了</strong>，则不补偿，反之商家需补偿接手方<span style="font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#FF0000;"><strong>0.5金币/天</strong></span>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#444444;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#444444;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<strong>例：1、任务收货时间为48小时，平台<span style="font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#FF0000;">倒计时归零</span>后，物流在倒计时归零后<span style="font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#FF0000;">24小时内到</span>，不补偿。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#444444;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<strong>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2、<strong>任务收货时间为48小时</strong>，平台倒计时归零后，物流在<span style="font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#FF0000;">24小时内还未到</span>，开启补偿</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#444444;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<strong>&nbsp; &nbsp;假设已超过40小时，则补偿金币为：1个。</strong><strong>不足24小时计为一天。</strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#444444;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#444444;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<strong>接手维权操作</strong>：等待物流被签收后确认收货，然后在平台任务处提起申诉（选择“<strong>投诉发布方：收货时间到后物流未签收超过24小时，申请补偿金币！</strong>”）上传<span style="font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#FF0000;">物流信息图片</span>以及此淘宝订单图片，客服根据图片中物流签收时间补偿接手方，从商家账户扣除相应金币至接手方账号，平台不收取手续费。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#444444;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#FF0000;"><strong>注意</strong></span>：有些<span style="font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#FF0000;"><strong>物流不显示信息</strong></span>，不在此补偿情况范围内，请<strong>联系商家</strong>协商处理。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#444444;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#444444;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<span style="font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#FF0000;"><strong>2、双方协商补偿</strong></span>：如若<strong>双方协商补偿</strong>，可提交意见处理，如双方协商补偿1个金币至物流到后确认收货。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#444444;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<strong>接手维权操作</strong>：由接手方提起申诉，提交双方QQ聊天协商截图，<strong>需截取到聊天窗口QQ号</strong>，否则无效，不予处理，平台不收取手续费。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#444444;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<h3 style="font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:1.17em;font-family:微软雅黑;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#444444;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	建议接手遇到此类问题，切勿心急，因为物流难以把控，商家也不是有意造成这个结果。\r\n</h3>\r\n<p style="font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#444444;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#444444;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<p style="font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#444444;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	<br />\r\n</p>\r\n<h3 style="font-weight:bold;font-style:normal;font-size:1.17em;font-family:微软雅黑;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#444444;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	----------------------------- &nbsp;<span style="font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-size:18.72px;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#FF0000;"><strong>淘宝长时间不发货处罚规定</strong></span><span>&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;------------------------------\r\n</h3>\r\n<p style="font-weight:normal;font-style:normal;font-size:16px;font-family:微软雅黑;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#444444;text-align:start;text-indent:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;">\r\n	接手方在<span style="font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#FF0000;"><strong>淘宝拍下支付后</strong></span>，由于掌柜长时间未在淘宝发货造成<strong>纠纷</strong>的，将处以<span style="font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#FF0000;"><strong>悬赏金币的</strong></span><span style="font-weight:inherit;font-style:inherit;font-size:16px;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:baseline;text-decoration:none;color:#FF0000;"><strong>30%</strong></span>处罚给接手任务方！任务可协商继续或取消。\r\n</p>', '', '', NULL, 1, NULL, 1, 1, 0, 1491152858, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, NULL, 0);
